URL: https://github.com/idiv-biodiversity/lcplants
BugReports: https://github.com/idiv-biodiversity/lcplants/issues
Repository: iDiv (https://idata.idiv.de/ddm/Data/ShowData/1806)
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
Imports: parallel (>= 3.5.2), utils
LazyLoad: yes
RoxygenNote: 7.1.0
Encoding: UTF-8
